<paragraph id="8BC636A1D174FFC668B22EF1FC6EFB4E" blockId="5.[174,1233,895,1850]" pageId="5" pageNumber="424">
T y p e l o c a l i t y. Underwater sandpit “de Kuilen”, Mill-Langenboom, province of Noord 
<collectingRegion id="49BDF843D174FFC669522EEEFEA4FB4E" box="[259,355,1183,1209]" country="Netherlands" name="Noord-Brabant" pageId="5" pageNumber="424">Brabant</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F36E7631D174FFC6693F2EEEFDF4FB4E" box="[366,563,1183,1209]" name="Netherlands" pageId="5" pageNumber="424">The Netherlands</collectingCountry>
